categories: Category:Unidentified members of the Ohnaka Gang

nodes.text: Around 20 BBY, this pirate informed Jiro that a ship's hyperdrive and main reactor were inactive. A little while later, when it turned out that Darth Maul and his brother Savage Opress were on the ship, this pirate, along with Jiro and numerous other pirates, joined them against Hondo Ohnaka. Later on, when the two Sith were overpowered by Obi-Wan Kenobi and Hondo, the remaining pirates reunited with Hondo, and helped him to acquire many valuable goods from the brothers' ship.
